extends ../app
block content
  div.page-header
    h1 Image Search Microservice
  

  blockquote
    h2 User stories:
    ul
      li User Story: As an authenticated user, I can keep my polls and come back later to access them.

      li User Story: As an authenticated user, I can share my polls with my friends.

      li User Story: As an authenticated user, I can see the aggregate results of my polls.

      li User Story: As an authenticated user, I can delete polls that I decide I don't want anymore.

      li User Story: As an authenticated user, I can create a poll with any number of possible items.

      li User Story: As an unauthenticated or authenticated user, I can see and vote on everyone's polls.

      li User Story: As an unauthenticated or authenticated user, I can see the results of polls in chart form. (This could be implemented using Chart.js or Google Charts.)

      li User Story: As an authenticated user, if I don't like the options on a poll, I can create a new option.
